{"questionId":"05468350-9fef-44ab-b9cb-893b50a7cadd_1","correctAnswer":"C","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Set up","content":"Substitute $d = 36$ into $1.5c + 3d = 108$."},{"title":"Solve","content":"$1.5c + 3(36) = 108$ $\\Rightarrow$ $1.5c + 108 = 108$ $\\Rightarrow$ $1.5c = 0$ $\\Rightarrow$ $c = 0$."},{"title":"Answer","content":"<strong>C</strong> is correct."}]}